column8: Patchy fog in the early morning. Cloud increasing during the day with a medium (60%) chance of showers, most likely in the late afternoon and evening. Light winds becoming west to northwesterly 15 to 25 km/h in the morning then turning south to southwesterly 15 to 20 km/h in the late afternoon.
Partly cloudy. Slight (30%) chance of a shower, most likely in the morning. Winds southwesterly 15 to 20 km/h tending southerly during the afternoon then becoming light during the evening.
Patchy morning fog. Mostly sunny day. Light winds.
Partly cloudy. The chance of morning fog in the northeast suburbs. Slight (20%) chance of an afternoon shower. Light winds becoming north to northwesterly 15 to 20 km/h during the morning.
Mostly sunny. Patchy morning fog. Slight (20%) chance of an afternoon shower. Light winds becoming northerly 15 to 25 km/h during the morning.
Partly cloudy. Medium (60%) chance of showers. Winds northerly 25 to 40 km/h tending southeast to southwesterly 15 to 25 km/h later.
